Package: dfdiffs
Type: Package
Title: This package compares any two rectangular data objects. 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Martin J Frigaard
Maintainer: Martin J Frigaard <martin.frigaard@bmrn.com>
Description: dfdiffs compares data.frames, tibbles, and data.tables and tells 
    you 1) what is here now that wasn't here before, 2) what was here before 
    that isn't here now, and 3) what's changed?
